{"tid":1301174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天水圍北區文宣組]拉倒建制派","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:11:40.000Z","uid":150,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"eded505a53a0c5fbf84e3c86e3dcc364c6073fe4","tid":1301174,"uid":150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打開過Post傾過想係區議會到拉倒建制派，<br />\n有見及此，我地人少少想做下文宣令到淺藍同埋對政治冷感既人多啲了解社會發生緊既事，支持一下年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一邊廂，都想聚集到一班人可以地區性地幫手宣傳點解我地要反政府既惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目前仲係構思階段，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎大家俾意見同埋加入文宣group<br />\n因為天水圍都幾大，我地依個group主要集中番天水圍北既情況。<br />\n依家好需要識得photoshop，畫畫，總之就係整圖既人；<br />\n同時都好需要大家整合資料俾我地做文宣！<br />\n有興趣幫手既巴打請入telegram group <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔入group既巴打都可以係post到留言，我地都會參考意見黎做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下為簡介：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8kgoyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8kgoyw.jpg&h=e6c0a676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYoE5MR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYoE5MR.png&h=4e493bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfGWoyx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfGWoyx.png&h=33ba2a3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"145ca742eb6d07654a999a337ae68e4c8c5dd31b","tid":1301174,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"有冇多d地方"},{"pid":"1b927c7c98ae553393c0aedd2026a45be3039cf5","tid":1301174,"uid":150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145ca742eb6d07654a999a337ae68e4c8c5dd31b","tid":1301174,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"有冇多d地方"},"citedBy":